(1014, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/''>WordPress 4.1 “Dinah”</a> <span class="rss-date">18. December 2014</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.1 of WordPress, named “Dinah” in honor of jazz singer Dinah Washington, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in WordPress 4.1 help you focus on your writing, and the new default theme lets you show it off in style. Introducing Twenty Fifteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Fifteen, is [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/whats-your-first-impression-of-distraction-free-writing-in-wordpress-4-1''>WPTavern: What’s Your First Impression of Distraction Free Writing in WordPress 4.1?</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/nulis-a-free-minimalist-wordpress-theme-with-a-unique-twist''>WPTavern: Nulis: A Free Minimalist WordPress Theme with a Unique Twist</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/phpbb-com-compromised-users-should-change-their-passwords''>WPTavern: phpBB.com Compromised, Users Should Change Their Passwords</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
